"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The Kintsugi testnet is live! I would like to introduce to you how to connect to Kintsugi with Metamask and make a transfer.\\n\\n**Remember:  Do Not use a wallet address that has assets on the Mainnet. Make a New   Wallet Address!** \\n\\n* **Open this website**: <https://kintsugi.themerge.dev/>\\n\\n  <https://kintsugi.themerge.dev/>\\n* **Click Add network to Metamask**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/aib0HQKJp64h7_vY65EsQ.png?height=946&width=1622)\\n\\n* **Click Approve and Sitch Network**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/VkCOzJIl_w24CV-iiD0YX.png?height=693&width=997)\\n\\n**Or You Can Add Testnet By Yourself**\\n\\n* Click Add Network\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AzrV0IL93Zj15tZASC6fu.png?height=757&width=440)\\n\\n* INPUT\\n\\n  Name: kintsugi\\n  RPC-URL: [http://127.0.0.1:8545](http://127.0.0.1:8545/)\\n  Chain-ID: 1337702\\n\\n  I noticed that sometimes I input RPC-URL: [http://127.0.0.1:8545](http://127.0.0.1:8545/) the web tells me the URL is Wrong\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Dv2S3GC1RSkGfnkXdwJzB.png?height=802&width=1209)\\n\\n* This is the right URL:  <https://rpc.kintsugi.themerge.dev>\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XjwRJbsgKaX-0dFGtobgM.png?height=794&width=1187)\\n\\n* **Click Save, Approve, and Sitch Network**\\n\\n**Now you can get some funds from the faucet:** <https://faucet.kintsugi.themerge.dev>\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/VM0j8aDWEX82uN-2VGEiK.png?height=828&width=591)\\n\\n**Enter your address and click the Request Button**\\n\\nYou will see 50 ETH in your Testnet Wallet soon.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Qk4UY7PTcbdoCRJIv6zQQ.png?height=621&width=443)\\n\\n**Remember:  Do Not use a wallet address that has assets on the Mainnet. Make a New   Wallet Address!** \\n\\nThen you can send a transaction just like using Mainnet.\",\"timestamp\":1639818806,\"title\":\"Connect to Kintsugi  Testnet and Make a Transfer\"},\"digest\":\"c7GjZthoJk3v-VmVqAeh3Vm8RDqlMn3y3D2wttnGNFY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x316e97Ee2238fF8808b7aabf2f283dCE219b9ca2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cjl4XOQUK2oPhTBFi5XPEyCu-41KncGcwbY_8e-KtkY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MxAPoKFLPU8Dw7vYfV4g7CXf1l_ORjl8fScYruUDYnc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3j4z_pnJ7GXm_qjLRAd-LO-1M-7HHrSVV1UYpXgZVXWbp028TsrHlG68iCVqP8tPwfdcAdm2Np1aYMqk0CLJWQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xedc351adde95c978acc8790c6fe0af13e9423e5ab061405d6a46cf88409ea7fe21b85672e5943a72e849cafec44dfcd4ed37bf757d04ef03ddbdbe82295b06051b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cjl4XOQUK2oPhTBFi5XPEyCu-41KncGcwbY_8e-KtkY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MxAPoKFLPU8Dw7vYfV4g7CXf1l_ORjl8fScYruUDYnc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"gA96sdkhNNQHlg_0tMkjbXrl6SLGffSx2sVaZ4TXyMA\"}"